      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been absolutely pampered and honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The paint is flawless, the interior still has that fresh vibe, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Swing by and take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2005 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the high-pressure VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014proactively addressing the platform's known structural requirements. It retains its factory-correct 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and M-Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains exceptionally communicative, featuring original Sachs dampers and a pristine undercarriage. The individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized, ensuring razor-sharp throttle response. This is an investment-grade example of the ultimate driving machine, preserved in its purest form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full documented service history and having been stored in a climate-controlled garage since day one. With no leaks, a smooth-shifting transmission, and tires with nearly full tread, this vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. It is a pristine, turn-key example ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. The vehicle\u2019s condition is beyond reproach, exhibiting a flawless aesthetic and peak mechanical performance. This is a definitive acquisition for the connoisseur seeking a vehicle in its most refined state, offering an unrivaled driving experience and investment potential.",
      "price": 48500.0,
