    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept in pristine condition inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
